eventDecorators.name: ClaimSubdomain
eventDecorators.description: Validator's status changed. Event emitted for each executed trade.

functionDecorators.name: register
functionDecorators.description: Register a subdomain with the default resolver if it hasn't been claimed yet.

parameterDecorators.name: _subnode
parameterDecorators.description: The hash of the label to register.

parameterDecorators.name: _owner
parameterDecorators.description: The address of the new owner.

functionDecorators.name: registerWithResolver
functionDecorators.description: Register a subdomain if it hasn't been claimed yet.

parameterDecorators.name: _subnode
parameterDecorators.description: The hash of the label to register.

parameterDecorators.name: _owner
parameterDecorators.description: The address of the new owner.

parameterDecorators.name: _resolver
parameterDecorators.description: The address of the resolver. If the resolver supports the address interface, the subdomain's address will be set to the new owner.
